8月25日，[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]北侧有飓风形成。气旋向西移动，从伊纳瓜群岛上空经过后于8月27日以二级飓风强度吹袭古巴北岸。风暴在穿越该岛逼近[[马坦萨斯|马坦萨斯]]期间减弱成一级飓风，但北上经过墨西哥湾后又重新增强成二级飓风，接下来又达到三级飓风标准。气旋于8月31日以二级飓风强度从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[巴拿马城_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马城]]附近登陆，此后在北上经过[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]期间快速弱化成热带风暴。次日，气旋从弗吉尼亚州进入大西洋，最终于9月3日消散。<ref name="hurdat">{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-05-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160512201021/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2012.html | year = 2012 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2012.html | author = Hurricane Research Division | title = Easy to Read HURDAT | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-11-20 }}</ref>

伊纳瓜有30套房屋被飓风摧毁，另有四人遇难。古巴海岸有多艘船只搁浅。<ref name="partagas-1" />佛罗里达州海岸沿线潮水高涨，圣约瑟夫湾（{{lang|en|St. Joseph Bay}}）的“佛罗里达号”（{{lang|en|SS Florida}}）搁浅后又被摧毁，[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]多条街道被淹。狂风暴雨对内陆部分地区构成重创，并以变得“满目疮痍”的[[玛丽安娜_(佛罗里达州)|玛丽安娜]]灾情严重。乔治亚州部分桥梁、水坝，以及玉米和棉花地因洪灾受损。[[哥伦布_(乔治亚州)|哥伦布]]有许多街道和便道被倒塌的树木封堵。<ref>{{cite book | author = Jay Barnes | title = Florida's Hurricane History | publisher = University of North Carolina Press | location = Chapel Hill, North Carolina | date = 2007 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dMx5bkZKxioC&printsec=frontcover&dq=florida%27s+hurricane+history&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAGoVChMIhZnysMH6xwIVxCUeCh0otwvS#v=onepage&q=florida's%20hurricane%20history&f=false | accessdate = 2016-11-20 | pages = 65–66 | isbn = 0-8078-3068-2 | archive-date = 2020-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201016082020/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dMx5bkZKxioC&printsec=frontcover&dq=florida%27s+hurricane+history&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAGoVChMIhZnysMH6xwIVxCUeCh0otwvS#v=onepage&q=florida's%20hurricane%20history&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>9月1日，诺福克一座教堂的尖顶被风暴刮倒<ref name="virgina">{{cite web | author = David Roth | author2 = Hugh Cobb | title = Virginia Hurricane History | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064635/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/valate19hur.htm | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-11-20 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/valate19hur.htm }}</ref>。
